{"title":"Macworld Podcast: Up close with the Apple Vision Pro","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2227402/apple-vision-pro-first-look-macworld-podcast.html","date":1707379200000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>The Apple Vision Pro is in the house! And in this episode, we talk about what it’s really like to use the new headset. Tun in to this episode and find out!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is episode 873 with <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Jason-Cross/\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Cross</a>, <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Michael-Simon/\" target=\"_blank\">Michael Simon</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Roman-Loyola/\" target=\"_blank\">Roman Loyola</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<div><div>\n<h2>Listen to episode 873 on Apple Podcasts</h2>\n\n\n\n\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div><div>\n<h2>Listen to episode 873 on Spotify</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div><div>\n<h2>Bonus content: See an Vision Pro Persona avatar</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As mentioned at the end of the podcast, the video below is bonus content. For this episode, Jason joined our podcast recording using the Vision Pro and the Persona avatar he created. If you’d like to see a Vision Pro Persona in action in a Zoom meeting, watch the video below. This was recorded before we started the podcast.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n<div></div>\n\n\n<div><div>\n<h2>Get info</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on the links below for more information on what was discussed on the show. </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2226459/apple-vision-pro-notes-from-the-future.html\" target=\"_blank\">Apple Vision Pro: Notes from the future</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2220040/vision-pro-experience-eye-tracking-eyesight-spatial-video-display.html\" target=\"_blank\">10 things I learned after my first Vision Pro experience</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"http